咖啡店长胡某诱骗十七岁女儿导致女儿服毒自杀。 女孩的叔叔李先生告诉记者，侄女小艳于 17 日服毒自杀，20 日去世。 家人在小艳的手机中发现她曾与瑞幸咖啡店长胡某交往。「店长他是 99 年的，已婚，还有个孩子。」李先生说，他利用职务之便欺骗我们这位小姑娘。 李先生提供的聊天记录显示，小艳向胡某提到自己两次怀孕。 视频截图 对此，辖区派出所工作人员称，公安机关已经处理了，但未透露具体情况。 瑞幸咖啡客服表示，没有接收到相关通知，门店是正常营业的。涉事咖啡店工作人员称，该店长已经离职。「17 岁女孩被诱骗致两次怀孕后自杀」，警方回应 _ 胡某 _ 李先生 _ 瑞幸"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dbe20e536044c65364663b688bea87e1_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "154 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665787016"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI6JrQyYCM34psEAMaCTExMDIzMDMzOSDLh8q2BjAAOIIBQARyCTY2NTc4NzAxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1725152078.898667", "card_id": "Q_665800531", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果为什么不对 12306 买票抽成?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "12306 买票明显是在 12306 平台上面的内购啊，为什么苹果不抽成 30% 呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665800531"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6JrQyYCM34psEAMaCTExMDIzMzM3MiCi8sq2BjAAOB5ABXIJNjY1ODAwNTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1725152078.899016", "card_id": "Q_660417619", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "各位认为文笔最